{"tid":2491731,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"連登巴膠每日關心善水東區大四喜元天屯赤開線日期暨清晨衝上慈雲山怒屌N3D老母專區","createTime":"2021-04-16T13:41:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T13:53:21.000Z","uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9e9997c77cfdac102dec8938b81447125de42879","tid":2491731,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:41:03.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><p class=\"center\"><span class=\"red\">連登巴膠專區</span></p></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP34AZitfRXibLu1z7qScbabEaVfM2sS89WpUHEeBKWqb?filename=qn41PQX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqn41PQX.gif&h=1b2c13e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQfKaJnfUa7UwupLvXREsJwLQzsHmr2LQkjryAjsQhgZX?filename=rDiU9QY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrDiU9QY.jpg&h=243f0bd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTc5cCLbpoeK6i26BQofn7Wezrc56WsYwLqLL2YeBRDEk?filename=vrsbsCE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvrsbsCE.jpg&h=5dcb34c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPMVGzXkvecoEoxE22zoJqpP6aETDbB1EThtprP9aCCnt?filename=M1yYR4j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM1yYR4j.png&h=31882cda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbG7uaRzf1UEf78A5pqwa3xdkwcj1qPi6m4acYHW8AJDP?filename=xGdBDKk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxGdBDKk.jpg&h=af11ffec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWBW94wc6N66BB9wE63b1M5PAhL2CPJsuGU986ZAdNJ3L?filename=EM1r0XG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEM1r0XG.gif&h=a8346622&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRqrJp34s4w6KhPBdvN5xLs6mZDJnP1J7ZWV4EmmSmnYi?filename=g8BPehH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8BPehH.png&h=12a266f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><br />\n連登巴膠專區三毛名單：<br />\n&bull; R730（歿）<br />\n&bull; 56185@258D - #271600<br />\n&bull; 秋本_五十鈴 - #54058<br />\n&bull; N700S - #57827</span></span><br />\n<br />\n宜：Block7、無視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n忌：回覆、爭論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n膠talk語錄：<br />\n<br />\n1） （路線號）班客搭（其他交通選項/行路）都得啦，係佢地咁鍾情巴士。（地區名）真係好令人討厭，條條線都用幾十部車霸咁多資源，搞到其他地區唔夠車用，應該全部減一半用車量就差不多。<br />\n<br />\n2） 你屋企樓下有全日（地區名）線就唔好係度講風涼話，係度盲反 ！！！！！你唔用（路線號）唔代表其他人唔需要搭，否則為什麼區議員和居民要不斷爭取？<br />\n<br />\n3） （鐵路接駁路線號）係阻礙（地區名）巴士路線發展的絆腳石，最好取消左佢，做好對外巴士服務。<br />\n<br />\n4） （起點）可以去（上車站位）搭（路線號），步行也不算太遠！<br />\n<br />\n5） （持份者）對（地區名）存有歧視及欺凌態度，鐵證如山，甚至早在（時間點）前已經出現，咩野（上述地區人士之戲稱）論，不攻自破。唔認同唔緊要，歡迎拎數據拎道理黎插到我口啞啞。拎唔到既，可以唔出聲唔使理我。又要出聲，又剩係識含血噴人人身攻擊，咁叫高質素既討論？除左含血噴人人身攻擊同留低個負皮，還有甚麼板釜？<br />\n<br />\n6） 呢度部分人只係識盲反（路線號），盲反（地區名）巴士線，非理性討論，毫無建樹，一啲出色都無。唔高興，意見不合就只係發惡話飛走（地區名），毫無建設性。<br />\n<br />\n7） 總之任何反對改善（地區名）巴士服務的人，就要被聲討。<br />\n<br />\n8） 其他人要求改善其他地區服務就得，我地提出改善（地區名）巴士服務就講乜都唔合心意，根本就係盲反。<br />\n<br />\n9） （地區名）點解可以做到大帝，獨攬（全/各）區所有（路線種類）線？<br />\n<br />\n10） （地區1）成為改線絆腳石囉，有條（路線A）都要死攬（路線B），呢啲咪真大帝囉。整個（地區2）對（路線B）既期望就係改快，改都唔改就取消，會唔會過份左啲呢？因為（地區名）反對，就要推倒，而（巴士公司）又要咁聽話，我真係唔知係乜野道理。<br />\n<br />\n11) 當個世界係圍住 (地區) 轉當正自己係地球中心的野，無野值得睇，但班人批鬥 (區議員) 就有問題。<br />\n<br />\n12）住(某地區）二線地區唔係仲諗住有跨區線呀？ 自己出（某地區）市中心轉啦"},{"pid":"5d2baf0ff3398758c74c966d765fe9083b7eb7c3","tid":2491731,"uid":38651,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:41:42.000Z","msg":"好彩標題無爆字數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22158486de7aa195f8643e005b60b97b1460e45","tid":2491731,"uid":155246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:44:29.000Z","msg":"原來批85xx過咗新巴咁就一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f20f389b0ee5c6060eb4d8d99af1a327bbc7547","tid":2491731,"uid":200210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:45:15.000Z","msg":"今期屎水開彩 2同23<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97a94155c1e60289c7caaf5cfdd8c9b70f5d1f5","tid":2491731,"uid":36261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:46:02.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"limegreen\"><span class=\"xx-large\">只往 傑明 <strong>54</strong></span><br />\n<span class=\"large\">Only to Kit Ming</span></span><br />\n<br />\n直梯同mmc請盡快行54短棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6064fc1300cb370c09464e527be22c0cbff9808","tid":2491731,"uid":277659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f20f389b0ee5c6060eb4d8d99af1a327bbc7547","tid":2491731,"uid":200210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:45:15.000Z","msg":"今期屎水開彩 2同23<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:52:45.000Z","msg":"執柒左佢啦<br />\n鴨仔由13年開8-9減到今日30<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a64bff1a5f3410b38fc6fd6c716e4e80718613a","tid":2491731,"uid":277659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6064fc1300cb370c09464e527be22c0cbff9808","tid":2491731,"uid":277659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f20f389b0ee5c6060eb4d8d99af1a327bbc7547","tid":2491731,"uid":200210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:45:15.000Z","msg":"今期屎水開彩 2同23<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gi